    "text" : "FINANCIAL PRODUCT LIST\n\n1. Iubaxh3n – Dream-Linked Investment Portfolio\nA cutting-edge AI-driven portfolio that syncs with your life goals and subconscious aspirations (using advanced behavioral data) to automatically rebalance your investments.\n\"Wake up to your ambition... and a smarter portfolio.\"\n\n2. Quorlium-9 – Personal Inflation Shield Account\nA dynamic savings product that adjusts in real time to inflation trends in your local economy, preserving purchasing power and offering scent-themed financial dashboards (just for fun).\n\"Re-scent your reality. Reinforce your wealth.\"\n\n3. Zyntrelux VibeCore – Emotional Risk Profiler for Investors\nA biometric wearable that helps you understand your emotional state during trading, suggesting actions or pauses based on stress, excitement, or overconfidence. Ideal for day traders and crypto investors.\n\"Feel what you trade. Trade what you feel.\"\n\n4. Draxynote 88 – Smart Contract Notary Pad\nA blockchain-enabled digital notepad for drafting, validating, and storing smart contracts in your own handwriting style. It answers legal/financial queries and connects with your DAO or bank.\n\"The thinking notepad for your digital assets.\"\n\n5. GlimmerPod X5 – Floating Financial Assistant\nA holographic financial planner that syncs with your devices to offer voice-activated budgeting, market briefings, and sarcasm-laced spending alerts.\n\"Your money. Your style. Midair.\"",
